name: AdvanceInsutechs
overview:
Established in year 1996, we, “Advance Insutech Industries”, are prestigious organization engaged in manufacturing and exporting Fibreglass Sleevings, Yarns, Cords, Copper Cables & Woven Cloth and Polyester & Cotton Tapes. The range offered by us comprises Fiberglass Leavings Varnished – B, Fiberglass Sleevings Varnished – F, Fiberglass Cords Twisted & Braided, Fiber Glass Flexible Copper Cable, Fiberglass Woven Cloth, Varnished Fiber Glass Cloth and Polyester Woven Tapes.

Our Product Range: We are one of the reliable names engaged in manufacturing, exporting and wholesaling a wide range of insulating material. Our comprehensive range comprises Insulation Adhesive F15, Fiber Glass Flexible Copper Cable, Fiber Glass Vanished Sleeving (class-b), Fiber Glass Sleevings (class-f), Fiber Glass Sleevings(class-h), Fiber Glass Unvarnished Sleevings, Resi Glass Tape, Polyester Woven Tape, Fiber Glass Cord and Fiber Glass Cloth and Tape.

Application Areas: Iron & Steel industry Power industry Nuclear Power sector Paper industry Petrochemical industry Fertilizer industry CNG/ LPG Pipeline projects Construction industry

Our Team: Experienced professionals Quality controllers Sales & Marketing executives Administrative professionals

Quality Assurance: Since beginning, we are offering qualitative products to the customers and we continuously striving hard to maintain the same. So, for the reason, our professionals strictly follow industry laid norms and standards while manufacturing these products.
